# Milestones:

1. Project initiation and planning
   - Define project scope and objectives
   - Identify stakeholders and establish communication channels
   - Develop project timeline and allocate resources
   - Set up project management tools and version control systems

2. System design and architecture
   - Design system architecture and database schema
   - Define API endpoints and data models
   - Create wireframes and mockups for user interface
   - Finalize color scheme, typography, and layout

3. Development
   - Set up development environment and configure CI/CD pipeline
   - Develop backend services and API using Codeigniter4 and PostgreSQL
   - Implement frontend components using React.js and Material-UI
   - Integrate token management using Ethereum blockchain
   - Implement storage solution using Amazon S3
   - Develop containerization and orchestration using Docker and Kubernetes

4. Integration with corporate systems
   - Develop RESTful API and GraphQL interfaces for integration with existing systems
   - Test and validate integration with human resources management systems, payroll systems, etc.

5. Testing and quality assurance
   - Perform unit, integration, and system testing
   - Conduct performance, security, and accessibility testing
   - Address and resolve any issues or bugs identified during testing

6. Deployment and launch
   - Deploy the system to AWS cloud services
   - Configure domain and SSL certificates
   - Launch the system and provide access to target users

7. Training and support
   - Develop user manuals and training materials
   - Conduct training sessions for employees and managers
   - Provide ongoing support and maintenance

8. Monitoring and optimization
   - Monitor system performance and usage
   - Gather user feedback and identify areas for improvement
   - Implement updates and optimizations as needed

# Estimated Timeline:

1. Project initiation and planning: 2 weeks
2. System design and architecture: 4 weeks
3. Development: 12 weeks
4. Integration with corporate systems: 4 weeks
5. Testing and quality assurance: 4 weeks
6. Deployment and launch: 2 weeks
7. Training and support: 4 weeks
8. Monitoring and optimization: Ongoing

Total estimated duration: 32 weeks (8 months)

